{"tid":1645582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"核彈都唔割？我屌哂你班連燈仔啊","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T05:09:20.000Z","uid":46341,"like":93,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe62e58d2cd5e86c836194c4b437d8b5a358770","tid":1645582,"uid":46341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"S小姐 一個女仔無父無母無屋企<br />\n仲好勇敢企出嚟面對極權<br />\n除低口罩以真面目講自己經歷<br />\n你班垃圾就係度人格謀殺 收兵 玩感情 搏出位<br />\n成日話核彈都唔割 屌你老母得個講字？<br />\n你睇下班黑警 人地做呢樣野做得幾好<br />\n你地就係度屌屌屌 臭雞講嘢都好信？<br />\n將來如果有第二個第三個S小姐<br />\n你班垃圾唔好屌人做咩唔企出嚟<br />\n就係因為你係柒頭喺度割割割啊屌你<br />\n<br />\nS小姐 只有你係同路人 你講我就信<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c8152f186ea0a7c69482b58a10758981863b046f","tid":1645582,"uid":46341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"ffa87a1b3e633fc2f03873ed51ccadcf782caf37","tid":1645582,"uid":46341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"ece4e7121f21b06aea51e066f32bde1bd772c77d","tid":1645582,"uid":46341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"72db8725d40cda21b8c31a42404e0c9d68df9bf9","tid":1645582,"uid":46341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"3f85a12246156d3e9319a3031d3a205485fe9e8b","tid":1645582,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"一齊陪佢投訴<br />\n理得佢做過咩"},{"pid":"3a2803c81c1c6a9b6f414917c19f6bb3b5f0e139","tid":1645582,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9cd79aadadb8c639c4be8953a963e32656e1300","tid":1645582,"uid":6310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"呢樣野藍尸真係好過我地好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm